<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>expert at something • expert in something</xh5><p> <i>expert at something—</i>a person who is very skilled at doing smth.: Dave knows how to communicate with sales professionals. He is an <u>expert at</u> complex selling and knows exactly how to get his messages across.</p><p> <i>expert in something—</i>a person who knows a lot about a particular subject: If he is an <u>expert in</u> the problems of bringing the space station and the module together, he will be invaluable.</p> </entry>
